      <title>格雷厄姆之死凸显了国会的年龄问题</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/12/us/politics/lindsey-graham-death-aging-congress.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[按照参议院平均年龄超过 65 岁的老龄化标准，这位南卡罗来纳州共和党人并不算特别老。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/12/us/politics/lindsey-graham-death-aging-congress.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 18:39:15 GMT</pubDate>
