    <item>
      <title>特朗普回忆起生前与林赛·格雷厄姆的最后一次谈话</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/12/us/politics/donald-trump-lindsey-graham-death-interview.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周日的采访中，特朗普总统讲述了他在去世前几个小时与参议员林赛·格雷厄姆的最后一次谈话。格雷厄姆先生听起来“完美”，他说。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/12/us/politics/donald-trump-lindsey-graham-death-interview.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 17:02:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党参议员、特朗普盟友林赛·格雷厄姆死于“突发疾病”</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/12/us/politics/lindsey-graham-dead.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[他的办公室称，他死于“一种短暂而突然的疾病”。在参议院任职的二十多年来，他始终致力于推动美国在海外使用军事力量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/12/us/politics/lindsey-graham-dead.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 16:53:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普为何未能在伊朗协议中确保霍尔木兹海峡的安全</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/12/us/politics/trump-strait-of-hormuz-iran-deal.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统签署了一项协议，伊朗称该协议使其控制了该水道以及全球能源供应。现在，伊朗军方正在暴力维护权威。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/12/us/politics/trump-strait-of-hormuz-iran-deal.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 16:43:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>林赛·格雷厄姆 (Lindsey Graham) 将于 11 月面临连任。现在发生了什么？</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/12/us/politics/lindsey-graham-death-reelection-seat.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南卡罗来纳州的法律规定，他的去世将引发 8 月 11 日举行的特别共和党初选，该州州长可以任命一名继任者，完成其剩余任期，直至 1 月初。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/12/us/politics/lindsey-graham-death-reelection-seat.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 16:13:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
